Darwin, Northern Territory. Our simple goal is to help people with disabilities live a life without barriers that enable them to realize their full rights and possibilities. We live by the motto, &ldquo;TRUST. LOVE. CARE&rdquo; and we deeply believe in making a positive difference for people with disabilities. Having a combined over 20 years in the disability sector set us apart and we are making a difference every day.&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;As a dedicated Service Provider, we have been supporting participants to maximise their potential in many ways. We utilise a person-centered support approach through active listening. Our foremost aim is to assist participants to achieve their NDIS goals and well-being plan.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;kt-adv-heading_0f4e98-12 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading&quot; data-kb-block=&quot;kb-adv-heading_0f4e98-12&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 10px 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; clear: both; font-family: Inter; font-weight: 600; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: var(--heading--letter-spacing-h2); line-height: 1.6em; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure); text-transform: uppercase; color: rgb(107, 20, 104);&quot;&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: calc(2 * var(--global--spacing-horizontal)); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;Conducting Client Care Assessments and Care Planning&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;Managing client compliance&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;Answer new client inquiries over the phone in a knowledgeable manner with the aim of scheduling a care consultation&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;Schedule appointments and in-home services to appropriate staff based on discipline, availability and geographical requirements&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;Coordinate the provision of quality person-centred care according to the client&rsquo;s needs, service/care plans and available funding in accordance with the budget&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;General administration with respect to tasks performed and recruitment of staff&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;Development of the business within the Darwin region&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;kt-adv-heading_40745b-47 wp-block-kadence-advancedheading&quot; data-kb-block=&quot;kb-adv-heading_40745b-47&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 10px 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; clear: both; font-family: Inter; font-weight: 600; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: var(--heading--letter-spacing-h2); line-height: 1.6em; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure); text-transform: uppercase; color: rgb(107, 20, 104);&quot;&gt;PREFERRED SKILLS:&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: calc(2 * var(--global--spacing-horizontal)); margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;Previous experience within the aged care/disability/mental health Care Coordination role is mandatory&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;First Aid &amp;amp; CPR are essential&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;Experienced in assessing and planning care needs within the community&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;Valid Driver&rsquo;s Licence&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;High level of computer literacy, with a sound understanding of Microsoft Office&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;An outgoing personality with high energy levels, good communication skills and a personable telephone manner&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;Ability to problem solve and think quickly under pressure&lt;/li&