nt-weight: 700; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;Apply&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: var(--wp--typography--line-height, var(--global--line-height-body)); max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;Please click the&amp;nbsp;&ldquo;APPLY&rdquo;&amp;nbsp;button, respond to the&amp;nbsp;questions, and attach a copy of your&amp;nbsp;resume and your responses to the selection criteria listed in this advertisement. If you need any assistance, please email&amp;nbsp;&ndash;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;mailto:hr@purplesupport.com.au&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; text-decoration-thickness: 1px; cursor: pointer; color: rgb(107, 20, 104); text-underline-offset: 3px; max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;hr@purplesupport.com.au&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: var(--wp--typography--line-height, var(--global--line-height-body)); max-width: var(--global--spacing-measure);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;**Purple Support encourages applications from Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander people, people living with a disability and women. **&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1, '2023-05-25 12:17:36');

